  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ allows users to attach, or bundle, items within a ticket, which charges customers a flat fee for a repair service while internally tracking the individual costs of parts, inventory, and labor separately. When an item is bundled under another item on a ticket, the price of the bundled item does not contribute to the overall ticket total. Instead, the cost of the bundled item, referred to as the Child Item, becomes integrated into the existing parent item\u2019s price. For example, bundling a part under a labor item allows you to remove the part from inventory without disclosing its specific cost to the customer.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: You\u2019ll need to establish a parent/child relationship for your items before you can bundle them on tickets.</p><h3 id=\"BundlePartsonTickets-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2837905412\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bundling Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932787785/Catalog+Items%3A+Bundle+Relationships+and+Bundling+Items+on+Tickets\" rel=\"nofollow\">Catalog Items: Bundle Setup</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"createlink\" href=\"/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=SCD&amp;title=Catalog%20Items%3A%20Bundle%20Required&amp;linkCreation=true&amp;fromPageId=2200764440\">Catalog Items: Bundle Required</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/2152726556/Catalog+Items+Auto-Bundle+and+Auto-Add\" data-linked-resource-id=\"2152726556\" data-linked-resource-version=\"18\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Catalog Items: Auto-Bundle and Auto-Add</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933672484/Tax+Calculations+for+Bundled+Items\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933672484\" data-linked-resource-version=\"15\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Tax Calculations for Bundled Items</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932591125/Catalog+Items+Device+Compatibility\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932591125\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Catalog Items: Device Compatibility</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Instructional - 0091cd.png\" width=\"750\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2200764440/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"BundlePartsonTickets-BundlingItemsonTickets\">Bundling Items on Tickets</h2><p>When a Parent Item has been added to the ticket, you can click the Bundle button (link icon) to add a Child Item. A pop-up will appear, and you can search for the Child Item you wish to bundle. When you\u2019ve found the item, click <strong>Add Item</strong> to bundle it to the ticket item.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2200764440/Bundle%206.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"355\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2200764440/Bundle%207.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>After adding the item, you will see it is listed as bundled with the above item and is flagged as such. The Unit Price for the Child Item is italicized since it has been absorbed into the Parent Item\u2019s price.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2200764440/Bundle%208.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"BundlePartsonTickets-RemoveaBundledItemFromaTicket\">Remove a Bundled Item From a Ticket</h2><p>To un-bundle an item, start by removing the Child Item first. Click the Remove Item button next to the Child Item you wish to remove.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2200764440/Bundle%209.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
